Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:32.57,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}{\an8}優しく差し込む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:36.66,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}{\an8}大きな窓の中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:42.71,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}君と出会った あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:47.01,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}遠くに感じた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:54.60,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}少しずつ並べた思い出は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:58.48,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}僕を温める
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:03.02,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}小さいな部屋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:06.15,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}繋ぐ心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:11.53,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}そっと教えてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:17.83,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}この季節が迎えに来たら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:24.50,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}君の姿　もう探すことも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:29.84,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}出来なくなちゃうんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:35.14,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}ずっと忘れずにいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:41.10,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}また君に会える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:28.65,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}阳光从树荫穿过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:32.57,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}温柔地洒落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:36.66,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}大大的窗户中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:42.71,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}与你邂逅的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:47.01,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}感觉有些遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:54.60,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}一点一滴累积起来的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:58.48,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}温暖着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:03.02,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}在狭小的房间中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:06.15,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}紧密相连的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:11.53,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}轻轻地向我诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:17.83,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}再次迎来这个季节时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:24.50,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}甚至连寻找你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:29.84,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}都无法办到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:35.14,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}我会永远都不忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:41.10,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}直至与你再次相逢之日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=============ED结束=============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都一直被保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.89,0:00:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然非常严厉 却也是相同程度地过度保护
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被身先士卒的老师 保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:20.03,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,第24节课 毕业的时间 by 赤羽业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茅野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是什么打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说哪里啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀老师 连头发都帮你梳好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是希望他先帮我整理下衣服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 那位杀老师饱含热情的治疗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定变得稍微有点乳量了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 杀老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为师累了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累倒的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露出了前所未有的满足表情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也前所未有的虚弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀者怎么能放过濒死的目标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们得手的机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乐的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会走到尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的教室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逐渐变得强烈的镭射的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有力而残酷地宣告着 计划并没有变更
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须由我们自己亲手了断
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也可以就这样不干涉 听天由命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请举手表态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想杀掉杀老师的有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 放下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想杀他的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾几何时 枪 匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有老师伴在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 我们的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是暗杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了守护着这份羁绊顺利毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对恩师该做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都如有切肤之痛一般 心知肚明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:56.58,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}杀老师弱点33 全班一起按住便可捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就无法行动了吧 杀老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 中村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还担心你们抓住我的力量太小了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了暗杀还是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都没有去深思理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年来一直被夸奖 被斥责 被培养着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的触手 我们再一次紧紧握住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领带下方就是心脏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一击 谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人有意见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这班里 渚是首席呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渚同学 从领带上面也可以刺下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到的当天 就开了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样一直破着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是最重要的缘分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 动手之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先和各位老师打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉娜老师 你不参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是获得奖金的良机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经得到够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小鬼们和你那里 得到了许多羁绊和经历
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的暗杀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你和小鬼们的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 乌间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为有你 学生们才成长至此的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后的日子 也请继续指导他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 虽然你让我吃了不少苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这一年的时光 我一生都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 杀老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 各位 终于到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个一个道别的话 24小时也不够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需多言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代替道别 我最后点一次名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:16.18,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz45.49\pos(606,410)\bord0}点名册
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请每个人看着老师的眼睛 大声答到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人被点过名后 就可以动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不会有人早退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这节骨眼上不应一声的话 为师就去自杀了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快开始点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.04,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(321,665)}杀老师弱点36 关键时刻不会安排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤羽业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矶贝悠马
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈岛大河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈野日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥田爱美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,片冈惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
