Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并深思熟虑过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狭间绮罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速水凜香
