Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:53.59,IN-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}您的教诲今后也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:59.18,IN-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}永远是指路明灯
